UTILES
======

Test de release
===============
sudo xhost +
docker run -it --rm --net host hgraciacrag/resleasetest:0.1

Para que no se ejecute directamente y poder hacer pruebas de desarrollo
docker run -it --rm --net host --entrypoint /bin/bash hgraciacrag/resleasetest:0.1

Whiteboard
==========
https://awwapp.com


branch refactoring-file-structure
=================================
sudo docker run -it --rm --privileged --net host -p 3000:3000 -p 3001:3001 -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY -v `pwd`/src/webapp:/app/webapp -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix  lm


entorno desarrollo
==================
Docker funciona, lanzado desde carpeta ngasp
En el docker development Ngasp no funciona si no se esta en /develop/webapp/
sudo docker run -it --rm --privileged --net host -p 3000:3000 -p 3001:3001 -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY -v `pwd`/develop:/develop -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix  development-environment /bin/bash

