GIT
===
gitk
git clone https://github.com/CRAGENOMICA/ngasp-workshop01.git
git checkout develop

para actualizar
git pull

https://help.github.com/en/articles/fork-a-repo
fork
git clone https://github.com/Hgracia/ngasp.git
git remote -v
git remote add upstream https://github.com/CRAGENOMICA/ngasp.git
https://help.github.com/en/articles/syncing-a-fork


para elimiar dockers
====================
docker stop $(docker ps -a -q)
docker rm $(docker ps -a -q)
dcoker rmi docker if


